2 ish cups of lentils (used a mix)
6 cups chicken stock
2 tbps tomato paste
3 large carrots
1 stalk of celery
1 onion

-standard mirepoix 

1/2 tbls oregeno
1/2 tbls basil
1/4 tbs coriander
1/4 tbs tumeric
salt to taste
2 tbs red wine vinegar

I cooked this with the leftover lentils we had. The soup came out great.

I think the key was simmering for over an hour. 
